close_reason: "Completed planned scope for M4 follow-up: remove deleted items from semantic vector indexes and preserved verification context for future changes."
body: "Delete mutations currently refresh existing item embeddings but skip missing IDs. This can leave stale vectors in configured stores. This task adds docs-first contract clarification, vector-delete execution support, and mutation refresh behavior that prunes deleted IDs."
